            "description": "Link a question from the bank to this session. Returns `409` if the question is already linked.\n\nSupporter must be the assigned supporter for this session.\n\n**Roles:** admin, supporter\n\n**Response:** `201` — returns session-question object."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Unlink Question from Session",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/questions/{{questionId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["sessions", "{{sessionId}}", "questions", "{{questionId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Unlink a question from a session. The question remains in the bank.\n\nSupporter must be the assigned supporter for this session.\n\n**Roles:** admin, supporter\n\n**Response:** `204 No Content`"
          }
        }
      ]
